text: Jochen Strobl (born 24 February 1979) is an Italian skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 2006 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Italian male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Italy Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 2006 Winter Olympics Category:People from Innichen
